    <item>
      <title>Version 0.4.0</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
<h2>What's New in 0.4.0</h2>
<p><strong>Anonymous analytics (opt-out)</strong></p>
<p>Toast now sends anonymous usage data and crash reports to help fix bugs and improve the app. This is enabled by default.</p>
<ul>
  <li>We never collect your Vercel token, project names, or personal information</li>
  <li>Turn off anytime in <strong>Settings → Privacy → Help improve Toast</strong></li>
  <li>Send feedback from the menu bar</li>
  <li>Automatic crash reports with a one-tap prompt after unexpected quits</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://toast.asit.space/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
      ]]></description>
